SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1917 as follows:
1. On Page 1, Lines 20 and 21, by deleting after the word “solar” on Line 20 and before the comma
on Line 21, the words “energy device” and inserting the words “power facility”;
2. On Page 2, Lines 1 and 2, by deleting after the word “solar” on Line 1 and before the comma on
Line 2, the words “energy devices” and inserting the words “power facilities”;
3. On Page 2, Line 3, by deleting before the word “land”, the word “agricultural” and inserting the
word “public”;
3. On Page 2, Line 3, by inserting after the word “land” and before the period, the words “that is
agriculturally zoned or land that is under the authority of the Commissioners of the Land Office”;
4. On Page 2, Line 3 ½, by inserting a new subsection D to read as follows:
“For the purposes of this section, a solar power facility shall not include devices used for agricultural
purposes including, but not limited to, solar-powered fencing or solar-powered water pumps.”; and
5. By amending the title to conform.
Submitted by:
_______________________
Senator Bullard
Bullard-CN-CA-SB1917
